</li>
<li>
<p><code>DRAG_LEAVE</code>: the mouse has left the window while a drag is in progress.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>DRAG_MOTION</code>: the mouse has moved in the window while a drag is in progress.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>DRAG_STATUS</code>: the status of the drag operation initiated by the window has
